name: my 7 little nightmares
description:
MP4 | 30s | 8,5“ x 11“ | sRGB IEC61966-2.1 

I noticed I am sleeping, I can feel your presence.
You are all around me, my 7 little nightmares.

I want to face you, want to open my eyes.
But my fear fights me, keeping me blind.

So I keep dreaming, feeling the same.
My 7 little nightmares, you never go away.
